query:
SELECT
    uid
FROM
    mihomo
WHERE
    EXISTS (
        SELECT
            *
        FROM (
            SELECT
                uid,
                light_cone
            FROM
                warps_departure
            UNION ALL
            SELECT
                uid,
                light_cone
            FROM
                warps_standard
            UNION ALL
            SELECT
                uid,
                light_cone
            FROM
                warps_special
            UNION ALL
            SELECT
                uid,
                light_cone
            FROM
                warps_lc) warps
        WHERE
            mihomo.uid = warps.uid)
    AND NOT EXISTS (
        SELECT
            *
        FROM
            connections
        WHERE
            mihomo.uid = connections.uid
            AND connections.private);
